walking outside the tent.

473
00:29:52,452 --> 00:29:54,353
But when I opened it, no one was there.

474
00:29:55,768 --> 00:29:58,710
Since then, whenever I
go camping in the forest,

475
00:29:58,895 --> 00:30:00,456
